schools.name: Cactus Medical Health and Technology Magnet Academy

data.description: Welcome to this charming residence nestled on a serene tree-lined street in the coveted Palmdale area. Property is 1,438 Sqft. This versatile home boasts four bedrooms and three baths, offering a spacious layout perfect for comfortable living.The main house features three bedrooms and two baths, adorned with ceramic tile and wood laminate flooring throughout. Enjoy preparing meals in the updated kitchen, equipped with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, including a stove, dishwasher, hood vent, and a convenient range with built-in microwave.Additionally, a separate one-bedroom, one-bath studio with a kitchenette provides endless possibilities, whether for guests, an office, or.? Relish the tranquil ambiance with newer concrete and masonry walkways surrounding the property, perfect for outdoor relaxation. Inside, recessed lights illuminate the space, highlighting the cathedral ceilings that add to the home's airy and inviting atmosphere.Don't miss the opportunity.
